org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.viewport

Class ExtendViewport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.viewport.Viewport
      • org.mini2Dx.core.graphics.viewport.ExtendViewport

  • public class ExtendViewport
extends Viewport
    Similar to FitViewport except the viewport will expand its size after scaling to fill the remaining space of the window to avoid black bars. A maxiumum virtual screen size c an be set if black bars are desired after a certain amount of viewport expansion.
